The contractor will close the off-ramp from I-40 Westbound to NC801 South from 9:00pm - 7:00am and the on-ramp from NC801 to I-40 Westbound from 10:00pm - 3:00am on Wednesday Night (05/05). These ramp closures are necessary to safely place asphalt pavement on the ramps. Detours will be utilized for these ramp closures. A link to the detour maps is provided below.&nbsp;This work is part of the&nbsp;continuing construction to&nbsp;replace the I-40 bridges over the Yadkin River and to widen and make improvements along I-40.&nbsp;As always this work is weather dependent and may be subject to change.
